name: 科丽安·罗伯茨
name_full: 科丽安·罗伯茨 Cory Anne Roberts
introduction: Cory Anne Roberts is half Italian and half African American, but she grew up in Bali with her father. Although she began her entertainment career in the modeling industry, she has hosting training from Marki Costello, improv training from Groundlings, and theatrical training from Sara Mornell, Saxon Trainor, and Ann Noble. She plays Zoe in the highly anticipated thriller, Model House.
